headline: ServiceNow (NOW) Stock Downgraded on Structural AI Concerns, KeyBanc Says
summary: ServiceNow, Inc. (NYSE:NOW) is one of the Buzzing AI Stocks on Wall Street. On December 15, KeyBanc downgraded ServiceNow to Underweight, flagging disruption risks around artificial intelligence, valuation and growth momentum as the enterprise software sector heads into 2026. While near-term strengths do exist for NOW, they are being outweighed by structural and competitive headwinds. […]
